ce<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tDoug heard the foot tapping of a few customers around him, and he could sense their annoyance. As if being able to read Doug's mind, one staff member finally made the wise move to take this particular customer with a long list of request aside to take the order as well as to double-check , ensuring there would be no mistakes. Perhaps instead of mind-reading, it was just that the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/agitation\" target=\"_blank\">agitation</a> of all the other crowd in the restaurant was just too overwhelming. With the time-consuming customer out of the way, the line was progressing along much faster than before.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/169144419860/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p810689/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p810689\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p825079/\">老外也跟风过中秋，中秋英文祝福语大集锦！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p823204/\">推荐：这个秋天，最好看的英剧都在这里了！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p771216/\">囧研究：为什么我们常说一日之计在于晨？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p794521/\">下一个莫扎特？！11岁英国音乐神童有多牛X？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p825024/\">希拉里晕倒健康状况成黑点 能撑到大选那天么</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p823252/\">跟新歌声学英文：It's a Man's Man's Man's World</a></l